<li><a href="http://pachelbel.net/works/index.html" class="external text" title="http://pachelbel.net/works/index.html" rel="nofollow">Pachelbel Street — Archives of J.Pachelbel's Works</a>, includes a complete catalogue of Pachelbel's works compiled by Hideo Tsukamoto</li>
<li><a href="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;sql=41:7804~T1" class="external text" title="http://www.allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&amp;sql=41:7804~T1" rel="nofollow">Johann Pachelbel at Allmusic.com</a></li>
