<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Johann_Pachelbel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: Recordings">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Recordings</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>Works by Pachelbel in MIDI and MP3 format at <a href="http://www.logoslibrary.org/classical/pachelbel/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.logoslibrary.org/classical/pachelbel/index.html" rel="nofollow">Logos Virtual Library</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ik.inf.unideb.hu/CantoArmonico/CD/Canto_Armonico_-_Pachelbel_-_Magnificat.mp3" class="external text" title="http://ik.inf.unideb.hu/CantoArmonico/CD/Canto_Armonico_-_Pachelbel_-_Magnificat.mp3" rel="nofollow">Recording of <i>Magnificat in D major</i> – for voices only</a> - By Canto Armonico.</li>
</ul>


